---
title: Pork Sausages & Herby Hasselback Potatoes with Mustard Jus & Charred Corn Cobs
description: Get ready for a mouthful of flavour and comfort! Savoury pork sausages are paired with crispy, golden hasselback potatoes, drizzled with rich mustard jus for that perfect finishing touch. Add a refreshing tomato salad to balance it all out, and you've got a hearty, satisfying meal that’ll have you coming back for more!
This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.
